age-link-expand\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container restack-image\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-refresh-cw\"><path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 0 1 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1 6.74 2.74L21 8\"></path><path d=\"M21 3v5h-5\"></path><path d=\"M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-9 9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1-6.74-2.74L3 16\"></path><path d=\"M8 16H3v5\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container view-image\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2\"><polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></div></div></div></div></a></figure></div><h2 class=\"header-anchor-post\">Engineering And Design (Going Forward)<div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-alignItems-center pc-position-absolute pc-reset header-anchor-parent\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset pubTheme-yiXxQA\"><div id=\"¬ßengineering-and-design-going-forward\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset header-anchor offset-top\"></div><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Link\" data-href=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/i/111839991/engineering-and-design-going-forward\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_sm-G3LciD priority_secondary-S63h9o\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></button></div></div></h2><p><em>by Aizea</em></p><p>Hi all, It‚Äôs been a tremendous month here at Endless Clouds. We‚Äôre working on a ton of really cool things internally and the engineering is progressing just as fast as we hoped since the last update.</p><p>For most of the last year, I‚Äôve been dissatisfied with our Engineering productivity and was aware that we had to make drastic changes to achieve the velocity required to ship our game.</p><p>Well, we made those changes and they are showing to be very effective. We‚Äôre able to ship and develop features internally at a pace we simply couldn‚Äôt before, with a fraction of the engineers at a fraction of the time. We‚Äôre staying lean, agile and productive, and we‚Äôve got a ton to show from roughly only a month‚Äôs worth of work.</p><div data-component-name=\"Twitter2ToDOM\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://twitter.com/TheTreeverse/status/1641782496412008456&quot;,&quot;full_text&quot;:&quot;A few of the things we've been working on!\\n\\n‚õèÔ∏èü™ìüé£ü§∫ &quot;,&quot;username&quot;:&quot;TheTreeverse&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Treeverse (üå±)&quot;,&quot;date&quot;:&quot;Fri Mar 31 12:40:24 +0000 2023&quot;,&quot;photos&quot;:[{&quot;img_url&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/upload/w_1028,c_limit,q_auto:best/l_twitter_play_button_rvaygk,w_88/kpcdjrbdqaobd1fnpcpi&quot;,&quot;link_url&quot;:&quot;https://t.co/FsNkFMEEtG&quot;,&quot;alt_text&quot;:null}],&quot;quoted_tweet&quot;:{},&quot;retweet_count&quot;:50,&quot;like_count&quot;:289,&quot;expanded_url&quot;:{},&quot;video_url&quot;:&quot;https://video.twimg.com/ext_tw_video/1641781480677310464/pu/vid/480x270/a8_e3eWqM78W-dL9.mp4?tag=12&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true}\" class=\"tweet\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/TheTreeverse/status/1641782496412008456\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" class=\"tweet-link-top\"><div class=\"tweet-header\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/twitter_name/w_96/TheTreeverse.jpg\" alt=\"Twitter avatar for @TheTreeverse\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"tweet-header-avatar\"><div class=\"tweet-header-text\"><span class=\"tweet-author-name\">Treeverse (üå±) </span><span class=\"tweet-author-handle\">@TheTreeverse</span></div></div><div class=\"tweet-text\">A few of the things we've been working on!\n\n‚õèÔ∏èü™ìüé£ü§∫ </div></a><div class=\"tweet-video-wrapper\"><video controls=\"true\" src=\"https://video.twimg.com/ext_tw_video/1641781480677310464/pu/vid/480x270/a8_e3eWqM78W-dL9.mp4?tag=12\" alt=\"Video\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"tweet-video\"></video></div><a href=\"https://twitter.com/TheTreeverse/status/1641782496412008456\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" class=\"tweet-link-bottom\"><div class=\"tweet-footer\"><span class=\"tweet-date\">12:40 PM ‚àô Mar 31, 2023</span><hr><div class=\"tweet-ufi\"><span href=\"https://twitter.com/TheTreeverse/status/1641782496412008456/likes\" class=\"likes\"><span class=\"like-count\">289</span><span>Likes</span></span><span href=\"https://twitter.com/TheTreeverse/status/1641782496412008456/retweets\" class=\"retweets\"><span class=\"rt-count\">50</span><span>Retweets</span></span></div></div></a></div><p>In the previous update, I mentioned that we were testing two architectures side by side, mainly hoping for the unity DOTs strategy to pay off and I‚Äôm happy to say that we have already validated it. Therefore we‚Äôre continuing full development of the MMORPG using Unity Dots on our server.</p><p>We‚Äôve cemented our networking and server architecture, we are confident it can handle the load and capacity we hope to achieve and I‚Äôm feeling extremely bullish on our current engineering strategy. It‚Äôs simple, effective, to the point and just gets stuff done.</p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Xa6H!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcee79746-7f10-4c1d-8696-a43ea50c53f3_770x450.gif\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel=\"\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Xa6H!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcee79746-7f10-4c1d-8696-a43ea50c53f3_770x450.gif 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Xa6H!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcee79746-7f10-4c1d-8696-a43ea50c53f3_770x450.gif 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Xa6H!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcee79746-7f10-4c1d-8696-a43ea50c53f3_770x450.gif 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Xa6H!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcee79746-7f10-4c1d-8696-a43ea50c53f3_770x450.gif 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Xa6H!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcee79746-7f10-4c1d-8696-a43ea50c53f3_770x450.gif\" width=\"770\" height=\"450\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/cee79746-7f10-4c1d-8696-a43ea50c53f3_770x450.gif&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:450,&quot;width&quot;:770,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:11539465,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/gif&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Xa6H!,w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcee79746-7f10-4c1d-8696-a43ea50c53f3_770x450.gif 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Xa6H!,w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcee79746-7f10-4c1d-8696-a43ea50c53f3_770x450.gif 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Xa6H!,w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcee79746-7f10-4c1d-8696-a43ea50c53f3_770x450.gif 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Xa6H!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcee79746-7f10-4c1d-8696-a43ea50c53f3_770x450.gif 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture><div class=\"image-link-expand\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container restack-image\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-refresh-cw\"><path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 0 1 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1 6.74 2.74L21 8\"></path><path d=\"M21 3v5h-5\"></path><path d=\"M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-9 9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1-6.74-2.74L3 16\"></path><path d=\"M8 16H3v5\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container view-image\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2\"><polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></div></div></div></div></a><figcaption class=\"image-caption\">A simple demonstration of 25,000 active monsters on the server</figcaption></figure></div><p>Going forward you will notice our art assets will look more generic. We‚Äôre doing this to focus on the important things first; shipping fun, game-worthy features. I hope we‚Äôve already proven our capacity as a company to produce high-quality art assets, and soon we will also prove our ability to engineer and ship features at a much faster pace too.</p><p>In the following months, we hope to tackle the start of our multiplayer PvE and PvP experience. We want to get feedback on the combat experience in PvP and raid modes as soon as possible. We‚Äôll take the feedback we‚Äôve already received from pre-alpha as part of our testing and hope to solidify our end-game content based on community feedback whilst we work on the story-driven elements and narrative internally via quests, progression and more.</p><blockquote><p>As an aside, we would like to share a perspective regarding the overall market sentiment and general doom posting on Twitter. The crypto space has been resilient in the face of extreme events that one might consider several black swan events. Regardless of what happens in the industry, our focus has been and will always be on the production of a fun, enjoyable game to enjoy with family and friends. We know that games are a mainstay in our lives in this day and age and that won‚Äôt change whether the dollar collapses or AI takes over everyone‚Äôs jobs. In short, we keep building.</p></blockquote><div><hr></div><p>Disclaimer: Please note that anything written in this document should not be taken as financial advice. Endless Clouds is dedicated to producing a fun, enjoyable game that integrates NFTs. NFTs are a new and highly experimental technology and should not be bought for investment purposes.</p><p data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://endlessclouds.substack.com/p/monthly-treeverse-update-16?utm_source=substack&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=share&amp;action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"ButtonCreateButton\" class=\"button-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/p/monthly-treeverse-update-16?utm_source=substack&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=share&amp;action=share\" rel=\"\" class=\"button primary\"><span>Share</span></a></p></div>"
}
